        <div class="stat"><div class="stat-val"><span id="cnt2">96</span>%</div><div class="stat-lbl">Renewal Rate</div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<section id="features">
  <div class="inner">
    <div class="text-center">
      <div class="sec-badge">Core Features</div>
      <div class="sec-title">Why BTC Signal AI?</div>
      <p class="sec-sub center">See instantly whether it is time to LONG, SHORT, or HOLD.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feat-grid">
      <div class="feat-card"><div class="feat-icon">📊</div><div class="feat-title">Professional-grade analysis, automated</div><div class="feat-desc">The same chart logic traders spend years learning is processed in 0.1 seconds. You only need to read the signal.</div></div>
      <div class="feat-card"><div class="feat-icon">⚡</div><div class="feat-title">Instant LONG / SHORT signals</div><div class="feat-desc">Based on a combined indicator score, the system automatically decides the best position—LONG, SHORT, or HOLD—and even shows suggested leverage.</div></div>
      <div class="feat-card"><div class="feat-icon">🎯</div><div class="feat-title">Auto-calculated entry, target, and stop</div><div class="feat-desc">Using ATR-based logic, it provides precise entry price, take-profit target, and stop-loss levels in real dollar prices.</div></div>
      <div class="feat-card"><div class="feat-icon">📈</div><div class="feat-title">Live Binance chart integration</div><div class="feat-desc">Includes real-time TradingView-style candlestick charts. Track BTC, ETH, SOL, BNB and switch from 1-minute to 1-day timeframes.</div></div>
      <div class="feat-card"><div class="feat-icon">🔄</div><div class="feat-title">Auto-refresh every 60 seconds</div><div class="feat-desc">The analysis updates every minute automatically. Stay on the latest signal without clicking refresh.</div></div>
      <div class="feat-card"><div class="feat-icon">🔐</div><div class="feat-title">Secure license-based access</div><div class="feat-desc">Protected by license keys issued only to paying users. No key, no access—and expired keys are blocked automatically.</div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="signal-preview">
      <div class="preview-bar">
        <div class="preview-dots"><div class="pd" style="background:#f04452"></div><div class="pd" style="background:#f5a623"></div><div class="pd" style="background:#06b66b"></div></div>
        <div class="preview-title">btcsignal.ai — Live Analysis</div>
        <div class="preview-live"><div class="preview-live-dot"></div>LIVE</div>
      </div>
      <div class="preview-body">
        <div class="preview-signal">
          <div>
            <div class="ps-badge">LONG</div>
            <div class="ps-name">Long (LONG)</div>
            <div class="ps-reason">RSI oversold zone · MACD golden cross · Above MA20 and MA50</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="ps-lev-lbl">Suggested Leverage</div>
            <div class="ps-lev" style="color:var(--text)">3x ~ 5x</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="preview-prices">
          <div class="pp-card"><div class="pp-lbl buy">Suggested Entry</div><div class="pp-val" style="filter:blur(5px);user-select:none">$70,840.00</div></div>
          <div class="pp-card"><div class="pp-lbl sell">Take Profit</div><div class="pp-val" style="filter:blur(5px);user-select:none">$72,450.00</div></div>
          <div class="pp-card"><div class="pp-lbl stop">Stop Loss</div><div class="pp-val" style="filter:blur(5px);user-select:none">$70,035.00</div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section style="padding:60px 20px;background:var(--card);border-top:1px solid var(--border);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);">
  <div class="inner">
    <div class="purchase-header">
      <div>
        <div class="sec-badge">Live Activity</div>
        <div class="sec-title" style="font-size:28px;margin-bottom:0">People are joining right now</div>
      </div>
      <div class="purchase-live-badge">
        <div class="pi-dot green" style="animation:blink 1s infinite"></div>
        Updating live
