    </div>
    <div class="purchase-list" id="purchaseList"></div>
  </div>
</section>
<section id="reviews" class="reviews-sec">
  <div class="inner">
    <div class="text-center">
      <div class="sec-badge">User Reviews</div>
      <div class="sec-title">Trusted by active traders</div>
      <p class="sec-sub center">Real feedback from actual users. No hype, just honest results.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="reviews-grid">
      <div class="review-card"><div class="review-top"><div class="review-avatar">😊</div><div><div class="review-stars">★★★★★</div><div class="review-name">ko***27</div></div></div><div class="review-text">"I was skeptical at first, but after following the signals, I started seeing consistent profits. The stop-loss levels are surprisingly accurate."</div><div class="review-tag">On 3-Month Plan</div></div>
      <div class="review-card"><div class="review-top"><div class="review-avatar">🙂</div><div><div class="review-stars">★★★★★</div><div class="review-name">bit***91</div></div></div><div class="review-text">"I used to trade based on gut feeling, but this completely changed my approach. Now I rely on clear signals instead of emotions."</div><div class="review-tag">1-Month → Lifetime Upgrade</div></div>
      <div class="review-card"><div class="review-top"><div class="review-avatar">😄</div><div><div class="review-stars">★★★★★</div><div class="review-name">trd***55</div></div></div><div class="review-text">"When a LONG signal appears, all key levels — Entry, Target, and Stop Loss — are clearly provided. It makes planning trades much easier."</div><div class="review-tag">On 6-Month Plan</div></div>
      <div class="review-card"><div class="review-top"><div class="review-avatar">😎</div><div><div class="review-stars">★★★★☆</div><div class="review-name">moon***k</div></div></div><div class="review-text">"I use the 4-hour signals for swing trading, and they've been very reliable. Not perfect, but my win rate definitely improved."</div><div class="review-tag">On 3-Month Plan</div></div>
      <div class="review-card"><div class="review-top"><div class="review-avatar">🤩</div><div><div class="review-stars">★★★★★</div><div class="review-name">jin***42</div></div></div><div class="review-text">"I can't watch charts all day, so the auto-refresh every 60 seconds is a huge plus. The interface is clean and easy to read."</div><div class="review-tag">Lifetime Access</div></div>
      <div class="review-card"><div class="review-top"><div class="review-avatar">😁</div><div><div class="review-stars">★★★★★</div><div class="review-name">won***78</div></div></div><div class="review-text">"I even recommended it to my friends. It's simple enough for beginners, and very practical once you understand LONG and SHORT."</div><div class="review-tag">1-Month → Extended to 3 Months</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
